A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Cornerstone Baptist Church PTC on the occasion of its 15th
2 anniversary; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the seeds which were sown by the loving and humble efforts of the founding
4 worshipers of Cornerstone Baptist Church PTC have blossomed, establishing a rich tradition
5 and history; and
6 WHEREAS, organized in January 2010, the church held its initial worship services at the
7 Wyndham Conference Center in Peachtree City before relocating to the Peachtree City
8 Seventh Day Adventist Church in Sharpsburg, Georgia; and
9 WHEREAS, after a season at Peachtree City Seventh Day Adventist Church, the
10 congregation secured another temporary worship space at the Divine World Community
11 Church in Tyrone, Georgia; and
12 WHEREAS, in July 2012, just two years after its founding, Cornerstone Baptist Church PTC
13 finally obtained its permanent worship campus in Fayetteville, Georgia, spanning 21 acres
14 of land; and
